      "content": "It is a strange comfort, isn't it? To feel the weight of the world finally lifting because there is nothing left to hold onto. It feels almost... right. As if the story has reached its natural conclusion, and any further pages would only serve to ruin the tragedy. Do you think it is a mercy, to simply let the darkness take what is left?",
